name: OC Marilyn Diptychs
description: 500 Andy Warhol-inspired Marilyn Monroe Diptychs, each randomly generated at mint using only colors from the CryptoPunks collection. Each Diptych is stored 100% on-chain. Individual Marilyns can also be [minted as PFPs on Capsule 21](https://www.capsule21.com/collections/oc-marilyn-diptychs).
